        <h2>Who Is Nordic Spirit For?</h2>

        <h3>UK Users & Market Leaders</h3>
        <p>Nordic Spirit was specifically formulated for UK and Northern European palates. If you're in the UK, Nordic Spirit represents the benchmark—the brand 40% of users reach for first.</p>

        <h3>Fruit & Berry Enthusiasts</h3>
        <p>Nordic Spirit's strongest portfolio is fruit and berry. If you gravitate towards strawberry, wildberry, melon, or citrus in other products, Nordic Spirit's flavour science will appeal to you.</p>

        <h3>Moderate Strength Seekers</h3>
        <p>Nordic Spirit shines in the 6–11 mg range. If you find extra-strong pouches uncomfortable or want all-day comfort without intensity, Nordic Spirit's Regular and Strong variants are engineered for you.</p>

        <h3>Consistency & Reliability</h3>
        <p>Some users prioritise predictability. Every Nordic Spirit pouch tastes the same, releases nicotine at the same rate, and performs reliably. If you've found a Nordic Spirit flavour you love, you'll find it again.</p>
