        <p>Neither is objectively "better"—they're different. Try both and see which aligns with your taste and strength needs. Read our comparison: <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-for-beginners-2026">Best Nicotine Pouches for Beginners 2026</a>.</p>
